    "description": "<p>It can only be used when one or more of your [Hand Slots] are empty.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Assuming that you get any number from 1 to 6 on the drop item roll, you will receive one type of target drop item. It cannot be used multiple times on a target that has already received a drop item in the same Scenario.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>(Critical): The [Hate] value of this skill is 0, you can obtain up to two different types of dropped items instead of one.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A special skill that allows you to use your free hand to steal items from enemies who are distracted by their weapons.</p>",
